				<p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted);">Each step below is an assumption, not a measured figure. The ranges reflect the spread between a difficult early pilot and a product with established trust. The base case is used for the revenue model; the scenario table below shows how the output changes if the assumptions move.</p>

